---
title: Mediterranean Falafel Bowl (v) with Freekah Salad and Dill Yoghurt Dressing
description: Packed with fresh flavours and good-for-you ingredients, our Mediterranean inspired falafel bowl is the perfect recipe for a balanced dinner at home. Because of their texture, chickpeas are a great thing to use when making homemade falafel as they can hold their shape and work brilliantly when combined with fresh herbs and spices. To keep you feeling full, we’ve served the falafel with two delicious salads, roasted red peppers, nutty freekeh and a dill yoghurt dressing.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/mediterranean-falafel-bowl-ec3196d7-94b068fd.jpg
